born as they learn how to walk.\nBut you'll be able to save all the slippers.\n\nA new concept of shooting puzzle game.\nIt is a shooting puzzle game that makes a way for AI characters wandering in a maze to move easily and safely.\n\n100 stages with various solutions.\nVarious maze shapes, slippers, objects, and daemons are combined, so each stage can be played differently each time.", "short_description": "Save the slippers that are hanging in the maze of nightmares!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "(\ub370\ubaa8)(\ud55c\uae00)3000_900.png", "id": "429007318575366", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003276_429007321908699_4258283118475983943_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LvFhzUVgoMsQ7kNvgGd_Das&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCRUo4cbV5s27T5XYNyqzUUefA5tm6wBGOhhE8G2itgWg&oe=670E58AA"}, {"file_name": "\ub354\ud074\ub77c\uc774\uc5b8\ud2b8\ub85c\uace0(\ud55c\uae00).png", "id": "3213236945564295", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974517_3213236948897628_4786406447797518072_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2J539g_QHZMQ7kNvgHiK-WU&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYASU-yQ4mxTonVF4W0l7IZuVbOdJq5WEHAvxMMuf7IeEA&oe=670E6B5E"}, {"file_name": "(\ub370\ubaa8)(\ud55c\uae00)2560_1440.png", "id": "1042171706627527", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75429288_1042171713294193_695814847444454466_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qrA9RjXqEYEQ7kNvgEFhjDj&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDbnXTgr0dE0Rip7uVf9u3gBi6nzWVpokXGo3TWt_DXWA&oe=670E5A31"}, {"file_name": "(\ub370\ubaa8)(\ud55c\uae00)1080_360.png", "id": "938165583721864", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75195905_938165587055197_7689133019531011071_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_s